---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="书籍 — 像企业家一样写作">
  <div class="book-page">
    <div class="book-inner">

      <!-- Book 1: 选择改变命运 -->
      <div id="book1" class="book-section">
        <div class="book-hero">
          <div class="book-cover">
            <img src="/images/book1-cover.png" alt="选择改变命运" class="book-cover-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="book-details">
            <h1>《选择改变命运：靠学识赢得未来》</h1>
            <p class="tagline">靠学识赢得未来</p>
            <p class="motto">「善战之人，先胜，而后战」</p>
            <p>人生由十几个重大选择和无数微小选择构成。在重大选择面前做出最优选择，在微小选择面前养成好习惯——这就是改变命运的方法。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapters">
          <h2>全书十六章</h2>
          <div class="chapter-grid">
            <a href="/blog/fate-why-choice-matters" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">01</span><div><strong>为什么选择如此重要</strong><p>选择的滞后效应</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-how-brain-works" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">02</span><div><strong>大脑"机器"是怎么运行的</strong><p>习惯的脑科学原理</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-acceptance-first-law" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">03</span><div><strong>接受是改变的第一法则</strong><p>认知失调、自我预言实现、意义疗法</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-habit-of-investing" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">04</span><div><strong>"投资"的习惯</strong><p>再生产的习惯，让时间为你工作</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-habit-of-slack" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">05</span><div><strong>留出余闲的习惯</strong><p>钱、时间和精力的余闲</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-habit-of-open-mind" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">06</span><div><strong>开放头脑的习惯</strong><p>从各个角度和利益方看问题</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-habit-of-self-comparison" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">07</span><div><strong>和自己比较的习惯</strong><p>过去的自己 vs 现在的自己</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-habit-of-lifelong-learning" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">08</span><div><strong>终身学习的习惯</strong><p>实用的学习工具和方法</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-think-second-order" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">09</span><div><strong>思考后续的后续结果</strong><p>直接结果可能是诱惑</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-how-to-make-good-choices" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">10</span><div><strong>如何做出优质的选择</strong><p>选项、题目与方法</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-economics-of-choice" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">11</span><div><strong>经济学：关于选择的科学</strong><p>用经济学思维做决策</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-trends-and-opportunities" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">12</span><div><strong>趋势、机会与红利风口</strong><p>识别和把握时代机遇</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-centenarian-life-city-industry" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">13</span><div><strong>百岁人生、城市与行业</strong><p>时间成本最大、机会成本最大的选择</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-human-nature-in-choices" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">14</span><div><strong>影响选择的三种人性</strong><p>从众、短视与确定性</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-effort-and-luck" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">15</span><div><strong>再谈努力与制造好运</strong><p>努力的方式比程度更重要</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/fate-rapid-learning-method" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">16</span><div><strong>快速入门的方法</strong><p>如何快速进入一个新领域</p></div></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider -->
      <div class="book-divider"></div>

      <!-- Book 2: 第一个100块 -->
      <div id="book2" class="book-section">
        <div class="book-hero">
          <div class="book-cover">
            <img src="/images/book2-cover.png" alt="第一个100块" class="book-cover-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="book-details">
            <h1>《闭环："第一个100块"七步曲》</h1>
            <p class="tagline">从0到1的内容变现闭环</p>
            <p class="motto">「成长才是最大的副产品」</p>
            <p>用企业家思维重新理解写作。不是教你写爆款文章，而是教你建立从内容到收入的完整闭环。七个步骤，每一步都是真实踩过的坑。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapters">
          <h2>七步曲</h2>
          <div class="chapter-grid">
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-important-logic" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">01</span><div><strong>一个重要的逻辑</strong><p>选择具有滞后效应</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-money-tree" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">02</span><div><strong>一棵摇钱树苗</strong><p>找到你的内容赛道</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-how-to-get-audience" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">03</span><div><strong>如何获得观众？</strong><p>从0开始积累读者</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-byproduct-of-growth" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">04</span><div><strong>成长的副产品</strong><p>追着钱跑不如让收入自然发生</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-serve-your-audience" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">05</span><div><strong>为观众提供服务</strong><p>把读者变成付费用户</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-earn-while-you-sleep" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">06</span><div><strong>在你睡觉的时候赚钱</strong><p>构建被动收入系统</p></div></a>
            <a href="/blog/first-100-yuan-million-year" class="chapter-item"><span class="chapter-num">07</span><div><strong>年入百万</strong><p>规模化与长期主义</p></div></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
